
									[[   Exporting Image From Timely LXCSnapshot POC ]]



Problem Def:

	We need to export a snapshot as tar.gz file of a jenkins Container


Simulations Done:

	Step 1: Creating a LXC Container for Jenkins

			lxc launch ubuntu:16.04 jenkins


	Step 2: Setup Jenkins on this container

			( Make sure the gpgkey and repository is added and updatee)

			apt install jenkins -y 4
			systemctl start jenkins 
			systemctl enable jenkins

	Step 3: Create a snapshot of the running container 

			 lxc snapshot jenkins jenkinsSnapshot

			 lxc info jenkins 

			 lxc publish jenkins/jenkinsSnapshot --alias JenkinsBakup

			 lxc image export JenkinsBakup


